  <h2>Streaming FAQ’s</h2>
<b>How do I access ASCD Streaming?</b>
<p>Sign in with your ASCD log-in or create a new account.  <a href="http://streaming.ascd.org/">
Access ASCD Steaming</a>
<b>Does ASCD Streaming work on all devices?</b>
<p>You can access ASCD Streaming on your PC, tablet, or mobile phone.<p>
<b>Where can I find a list of all of the videos in ASCD Streaming?</b>
<p>The list of video programs available in ASCD Streaming will be updated as new titles are added.
  <a href="http://streaming.ascd.org/view-all">See the full list</a> 
 <p>
<b>How long are the videos?</b>
<p>Most videos are 60 to 90 minutes and designed to be viewed in a single session. 
  You can also pause your video at any time and return to it during the rental or subscription period.</p>
<b>Can I pay for ASCD Streaming by Purchase Order?</b>
<p>A purchase order form for ASCD Streaming is in development 
  and will be posted soon in the pricing section on the main ASCD Streaming page.<p>
<b>Are Videos Closed Captioned?</b>
<p>Yes, all videos have a closed captioned option.</p>
<b>Do you have any free videos?</b>
<p>Yes, check out the Teachers Lounge.</p>
<b>What if I have technical questions?</b>
<p>If you have technical issues or questions about ASCD Streaming, call 1-800-933-ASCD (2723),
press “5” or email: <a href="mailto:webhelp@ascd.org">webhelp@ascd.org</a></p>
<p>For Billing questions, please call 1-800-933-2723, press “1” or 
  email <a href="mailto:member@ascd.org">member@ascd.org</a><p>
<b>Do you provide a discount if I’m a member of ASCD?</b>
<p>Yes, you will receive a 10% discount upon checkout.</p>
